{"tid":117912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國母子戲院大聲傾偈 遭觀眾掌摑圍毆","createTime":"2017-02-12T15:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T04:17:43.000Z","uid":122,"like":121,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b41d3b1cfae602bd946d84c57b6057f65b032fc9","tid":117912,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>強國母子戲院大聲傾偈 遭觀眾掌摑圍毆</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-12 22:55:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n到戲院看電影，相信大部份都希望能有一個寧靜環境欣賞。然而面對有人大聲喧嘩，尤其喧嘩的是小孩，相信要靠同行親友的勸導，否則隨時釀成不愉快事件。<br />\n<br />\n年初二，山東淄博穆姓婦人帶兒子看3D電影，期間二人大聲對話，引起其他觀眾不滿。有一名女子竟出手掌摑小孩。穆女士不甘兒子被打，與對方理論。打人者與兩名同行女子合力毆打穆女士兩母子，導致二人受傷。　<br />\n<br />\n事後，戲院職員表示由於映廳沒有閉路電視，故未有拍下出打人者的容貌，而戲院的閉路電視只拍下打人者離開戲院的情景。穆女士深感無奈，只好報警求助。然而，戲院職員卻指當日穆女士的兒子聲浪確實擾人，引起其他觀眾不滿。"},{"pid":"ca8048a7d6461514f22cb945962f9e22cfc67e88","tid":117912,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"職員有都話冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84aef3a7430031d59161245eec6e06b04611103a","tid":117912,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d536c1be8711883b806e38cc73696a14927430e7","tid":117912,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>職員有都話冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n穆女士沒有後台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb4da334671b8c37033f358e45316f7a1cee7cc","tid":117912,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef90fc341c23dfb3c8a815c4238e5c8dbc6fcc3","tid":117912,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\